name: November 5th
description:
Guy Fawkes and his group who is GunpowderPlot planned to assassinate King James. The authorities were prompted by an anonymous letter to search Westminster Palace during the early hours of day, and they found Fawkes guarding the explosives.
Guy Fawkes is arrested on November 5th. 
5 November began to be celebrated. After a while, this day was called Guy Fawkes Night. Guy Fawkes Day had become an enjoyable social commemoration. The present-day Guy Fawkes Night is usually celebrated at large organised events.
